earing up for theOlympicsin style, having completed an impressive 200m butterfly and breaststroke double at the French trials on the same day - a feat he hopes to achieve atParis 2024this summer.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9998611726893494, \"rank\": 0.000134418280914828, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6432115529748657, \"rank\": 0.5415590189253549, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsin style\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"an impressive 200m\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"butterfly\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the same day\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old Marchand, who is based in the US, made light work of jet lag and the competition to swim the 200m butterfly final in 1:54.08 - the fourth-best performance of the season.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9998611726893494, \"rank\": 0.000134418280914828, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uni