, the heats and semi-finals for both races will be on 30 July, with the finals scheduled for the next day.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"semi\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"both races\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"30 July\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"the next day\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Marchand easily beat his rivals in Chartres on Wednesday, some improvements will be needed if he is to become the first swimmer to achieve the 200m breaststroke/butterfly double at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chartres\", \"score\": 0.99999999831698, \"rank\": 1.5262028111580531e-09, \"text\": \"Chartres\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chartres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chartres\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"some improvements\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the first swimmer\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke/butterfly\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some adjustments need to be made, we have to be careful,\\\" Marchand's French coach Nicolas Castel told sports dailyL'Equipe.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6432115529748